songs.title: Shady Narcotics
songs.lyrics:
[Intro / Spoken: Eminem]
Yeah!
God damn!
Feels like a long time don't it?
Did you miss us?
We missed you!
Ha!
Shady Narcotics
It's the Re-Up
Pussies!
And we're back
Myself
D12
50 Cent
Obie Trice
Stat Quo
And I would also like to introduce
The two newest members of the family
One goes by the name of Bobby Creek
The other goes by the name of Ca$his, from Orange County
And I think it's about time we just cut the bullshit, let's go!
